  "content": "<p data-pid=\"rmwPo1jI\">记笔记，最重要的是<b>理解</b>和<b>复习</b>。</p><p data-pid=\"3gFLVtqB\">如何理解？对所学的知识进行提问，并用自己的话来回答。</p><p data-pid=\"5_W5eEPN\">如何复习？将笔记做成问答的形式，时不时拿出来自测。</p><p data-pid=\"t4f_702C\">以最简单的英语笔记为例：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6bed12ca65110314dbee9f0b5ba399ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"4608\" data-rawheight=\"2176\" data-original-token=\"v2-4c5f48b51a62e3958693dcef5d05fa40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-da1218e99ffc7190d4c189a61e34b392_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"4608\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6bed12ca65110314dbee9f0b5ba399ad_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;4608&#39; height=&#39;2176&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"4608\" data-rawheight=\"2176\" data-original-token=\"v2-4c5f48b51a62e3958693dcef5d05fa40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-da1218e99ffc7190d4c189a61e34b392_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"4608\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6bed12ca65110314dbee9f0b5ba399ad_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6bed12ca65110314dbee9f0b5ba399ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"-is6SfKD\">理论上，所有学科都能用这种记笔记的方法。但是，说起来容易做起来难。没有任何指导的情况下，谁知道该提出什么问题？就算做成了问答形式的笔记，又有多少人会重复的去自测呢？</p><p data-pid=\"DlEH6Hd6\">为了更好的落实这种记笔记的方法，我也看过许多方法论，试用过不少笔记软件。但是都难以完美实现上述流程。</p><p data-pid=\"ef28PtM0\">直到高二下的时候，我在 GitHub 上找到了一款开源免费的复习软件—— Anki，这个流程流畅的跑起来了。</p><p data-pid=\"1dlz1l3w\">我简单的介绍一下，Anki 是一款自带间隔重复算法的卡片式复习软件。</p><p data-pid=\"wRh8a9xe\">下图是 Anki 的首页，每一条笔记都能做成卡片，而牌组是卡片的集合：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-444f286b932d34958b46a8e8ed421df3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1032\" data-original-token=\"v2-18bcfc89db1af98611fa3b0477ca407e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5f45240b7bd4d82e971dc4710414c6b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-444f286b932d34958b46a8e8ed421df3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1032&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1032\" data-original-token=\"v2-18bcfc89db1af98611fa3b0477ca407e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5f45240b7bd4d82e971dc4710414c6b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-444f286b932d34958b46a8e8ed421df3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-444f286b932d34958b46a8e8ed421df3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"v2JSda0-\">下图是添加笔记，类型是你想要的卡片模板，Anki 会按照模板帮你把笔记变成复习卡片</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-38c56f319ffc49030af8a9daab653e05_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-e7b55a8ede15dcb5e4522aaad8e39ce4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e809686752841395fed3bc081f7fcdd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-38c56f319ffc49030af8a9daab653e05_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1030&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-e7b55a8ede15dcb5e4522aaad8e39ce4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e809686752841395fed3bc081f7fcdd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-38c56f319ffc49030af8a9daab653e05_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-38c56f319ffc49030af8a9daab653e05_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"xNQKwRGS\">点击浏览可以看到所有的笔记，还可以预览笔记变成卡片后的效果：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a4079733232fa574fde92aebef11d59c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-5ba1581f36dee4e3763c171801f89ac0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-64cf1efd2d2d9079e441a697aa3406bd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a4079733232fa574fde92aebef11d59c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1030&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-5ba1581f36dee4e3763c171801f89ac0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-64cf1efd2d2d9079e441a697aa3406bd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a4079733232fa574fde92aebef11d59c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a4079733232fa574fde92aebef11d59c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"kYKwH6tw\">在首页点击牌组开始学习，Anki 就会把一张一张卡片糊到你脸上，让你赶紧回忆答案：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4cd0cdc383d7500d9c8e2f4e956bc65_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-ae2e4578eee789aab4762fdda8076b30\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7f9397327ce057d0364cf83236719413_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f4cd0cdc383d7500d9c8e2f4e956bc65_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1030&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1030\" data-original-token=\"v2-ae2e4578eee789aab4762fdda8076b30\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7f9397327ce057d0364cf83236719413_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f4cd0cdc383d7500d9c8e2f4e956bc65_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f4cd0cdc383d7500d9c8e2f4e956bc65_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"uVoRRypy\">在心中准备好答案后可以点显示答案，然后对比检验自己的记忆情况，然后选择这张卡片下一次自测的时间：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-320c19c535c24508eeedac04f29b4e8e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1027\" data-original-token=\"v2-ba6166071a6b77cc1291cd38a919c9f5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f10b1ee0983c51d82d4e1ab818c7e030_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-320c19c535c24508eeedac04f29b4e8e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1027&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1920\" data-rawheight=\"1027\" data-original-token=\"v2-ba6166071a6b77cc1291cd38a919c9f5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f10b1ee0983c51d82d4e1ab818c7e030_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1920\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-320c19c535c24508eeedac04f29b4e8e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-320c19c535c24508eeedac04f29b4e8e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"geRxUkvA\">并且 Anki 有安卓端、mac 端、iOS 端，我主要使用安卓手机，下面是一些截图：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt